- Nm 1990: Cng ty C phn i l Lin hip Vn chuyn c thnh lp, trc thuc Lin hip Hng hi Vit Nam.

- 2008: a vo khai thc 4 cng trnh quan trng: Cao c Gemadept, Schenker-Gemadept Logistics Center v 2 cng ti Dung Qut, Hi Phng.

- 2010: Nng vn iu l ln 1,000 t ng; a vo khai thc nh ga hng ha hng khng Tn Sn Nht; Nng t l s hu trong Cng ty Cng Nam Hi ln 99.98%.

- 2012: a vo khai thc Trung tm Phn phi s 2 ti KCN Sng Thn, Bnh Dng; Khi cng xy dng Cng container Nam Hi nh V.

- Nm 2013: Tng vn iu l ln 1,144 t ng, hon thnh v a vo khai thc cng container Nam Hi nh V.

- Nm 2015: i tn thnh Cng ty C phn Gemadept.

- Ngy 15/11/2017: Tng vn iu l ln 2,882,769,570,000 ng.

- Ngy 04/12/2018: Tng vn iu l ln 2,969,249,570,000 ng.

- Ngy 28/01/2021: Tng vn iu l ln 3,013,779,570,000 ng.
